      "content": "That definitely sets the mood. I want to push the \"supernatural\" side of it too. Given the specific vibe of this neighborhood, what kind of urban legends or local superstitions do you think would emerge? Like, are there certain things people say about how the community's history or the way they live might actually invite something darker or more sinister into the area?",
